Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since when were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water sploosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know, I don't think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I know that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know even though\NI don't think I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Spike, where the hell are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this ship was headed for Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are we on\NEarth all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, this isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're wasting time, our fugitive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first big one in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, why the hell are we on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The women are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you lead me to that\N"water sploosh" place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something very, tremendously,\Nwonderfully good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something very, tremendously,\Nwonderfully good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hot{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water sploosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have trusted you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I found Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed has been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35 point 38 point 0,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This! This, this, this!\N--35 point 48 point 1, 35 point 48 point 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I have your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm collecting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just the pinky one will do!\N--35 point 52 point 3, 35 point...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come on... can I have it? Please?\N--What are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ed{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really you... Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best way to make the kids listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ed from this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wandered in about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, she was eating with\Nus as if it had always been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about three years ago,\Nshe wandered away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if she was a cat or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how\Nshe was doing nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't think she\Nwould suddenly appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord up in the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the rest. Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you can stay longer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually looking for something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed knows where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just came here for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to gimme something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something good in\Nthe desk drawer over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside that drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that. Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whose{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came looking for Ed\Nabout 2 months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he forgot that he\Nhad put her in an orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he had been looking for\N7 years, hopping around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she will be able to meet him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People have to cherish what ties they have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Faye?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Sally Yung!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in your high school graduating class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a ghost.\NYou look just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, they say ghosts appear\Nin places where they have regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were put in cold sleep\Nafter that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you look like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember, Faye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, we gotta go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't know. Actually, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this course\Nchange without asking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plans have all been\Nscrewed because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't appreciate you\Ndoing things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to smell something really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they being so secretive about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're too hungry\Nfor their own good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans go insane if they don't eat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50 million...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appledelhi Siniz Hesap Lütfen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like one, Mackenroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Macintire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you, Mr. Appledelhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? Eggs are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, power and charge.\NThat's what's important, Macintosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Macintire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you can't ever\Nremember your assistant's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about\Nthe small things in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Macky-Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Macintire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally remembered where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone waiting for you, too.\NYou have somewhere you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go look for it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best thing, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50 million is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can eat sukiyaki\Nfilled with meat, then they--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faye went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did she go this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's heart and the skies\Nof Ganymede, was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Appledelhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come along with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperate with us if\Nyou don't wanna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?\NDon't interrupt our work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this Earth need\Nto regain a peaceful peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Earth of wild chaos! Is it the cosmos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a map! A map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, happiness comes\Nin the form of a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are creating maps to save the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, meteors fall often\Nand change the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're globetrotting.\NWe're chasing after every meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until every single meteor falls onto Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly adept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that you, Ed?!\N--Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Françoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that, and that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is father-person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Spike-person and Jet-person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, father. Good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was it daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, it's all right either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a token of my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Ed, were you the one\Nwho put the bounty on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty point zero, zero,\Nzero, zero, zero, zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 50 woolongs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Michael-duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Macintire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's dinner time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spike, dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come with me, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed is going someplace far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ein, you should go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come with Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too much time has passed by...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to lament that we were deeply in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind keeps blowing, while my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...cannot heal all the tears in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone, cry for me with parched eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real folk blues.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only want to know what true sadness is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sitting in muddy water...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...isn't such a bad life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if it ends after the first time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has a beginning... and an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is just a cycle of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With unwanted endings, becoming an adult\Nis to experience the inevitable finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a fast trip for {\i1}Bebop{\i0},\Nwith only two episodes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.74,0:24:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you pay\Nclose attention to how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "The Real Folk Blues (Part 1)."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:34.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Real Folk Blues (Part 1)"
